phrases: Oh, God, please save the soul of this girl with a broken heart!
Zoisite, committing evil deeds in a sacred place...
You are not getting away with this anymore!
In the name of God, Sailor Moon will punish you!
Gomen ne sunao ja nakute yume no naka nara ieru
Shikou kairo wa short sunzen i am about to sugu aitai yo
Nakitakunaru you na moonlight denwa mo dekinai midnight
Datte junjou dou shiyou heart wa mangekyou
Seiza no matataki kazoe uranau koi no yukue
Onaji kuni ni umareta no miracle romance
As you know, I am the sailor warrior of love and justice,
At last, the fourth member of our group appeared!
She is sweet and she is strong.
With all four sailor warriors together now,
it is like we are unbeatable now, you know?
Bring A Smile To Naru's Face!
Who in the world are you?
Once you find the Silver Crystal, everything...
Once you find the Silver Crystal, everything...
If I can get my hands on it, will it answer all my questions?
You have obtained one of the rainbow crystals already.
But, Zoisite, what is your next plan?
The Black Crystal already senses another rainbow crystal.
The next rainbow crystal is inside this man's body.
I shall leave it to you.
I do not think we will get to eat a chocolate parfait together.
You said we would eat a chocolate parfait together!
You are going to visit Naru?
She has not shown up at school for a week now.
I bet she still has not been able to recover.
I thought Naru was out because of a cold.
Honestly, you are just so dense!
Anyway, once we get to Naru's house, make sure to cheer her up!
If that is what you want, just leave it to me!
Sorry for showing up without any warning.
We were just sort of wondering how you were doing.
I was completely under the impression
that you were absent because of a cold,
but could it be your heart was broken or something?
What was that all of a sudden?
Do not you have anything else to say?!
Then why do not we go somewhere and eat a chocolate parfait?
You want to go out somewhere?
And maybe have something good to eat?
The power that could even blow up a planet?
In other words, apparently the Silver Crystal
has that much power, depending on how you use it.
So, where is this Silver Crystal?
I still do not know that yet.
But I found out that there are these shards called rainbow crystals.
That is right, the rainbow crystals are pieces of the Silver Crystal.
Of course, that is a story I heard a long time ago.
There were these bad guys in the Dark Kingdom
But apparently, someone trapped them inside
the seven shards of the legendary Silver Crystal.
With the rainbow crystals dwelling inside of them,
And having become humans, they led peaceful lives.
But Zoisite is trying to take the rainbow crystals out of them.
If he can take the seven rainbow crystals,
he can get a hold of the legendary Silver Crystal!
On top of that, it also revives an evil monster,
so the enemy is killing two birds with one stone.
As long as I am in this,
there is no way I will let those villains get their way.
That is what I was going to say.
But how do we find the people who possess the rainbow crystals?
The wand that I gave Usagi will respond to them!
In that case, I am against letting Usagi hang on to that wand!
You let her have it and she will just use it as a hammer
I do not think even she would go that far.
But she may use it for something close to that.
It is true that she completely lacks a sense of duty,
But that is why I want to give her the status of the leader,
I think if she is given an important role,
she will gain a little more sense of responsibility.
Please just acknowledge her as the leader!
It would be nice to see how things go first.
I guess Usagi just does not inspire people's trust in the end.
I still do not know much about her, so...
Once you get to know Usagi better, I am sure you will agree with me!
Everyone is here discussing something important right now.
Would you mind coming over here?
But I have to go to Chinatown in Yokohama
with Naru and Umino to eat tons and tons of good food now.
And at such an important time!
Excuse me, but what is wrong with you two?
You have been so quiet this whole time.
Miss Usagi, you brought lots of money with you, right?
but I guess there is not one for Mr. Nephrite.
I have never had it before.
I will finally get to taste the Peking duck I have always dreamed of!
So, you want to become a Peking duck that badly?!
No, I want to eat it.
I want to you to tell me!
Someone very precious to me died...
He suffered so much, but I could not help him.
You have a very beautiful heart.
I am sure that person's soul was saved.
But now that I have lost him, I have nothing left.
Love will be right next to you before you know it.
Turn around and you will find love.
If I turn around, there will be love?
Where in the world did she go?
Hurry up and take the wand out of your bag!
That wand is telling us the location of the seven rainbow crystals!
There is a chance a monster will appear where the wand is pointing to!
Use the transmitter to call Mako!
Okay, so the origin of the signal is in the cemetery?
Would not you rather learn more about yourself?
I am just a simple priest.
This Black Crystal here will tell us who you really are.
Please do not do any more bad things!
Please do not do any more bad things!
Why do not you worry about yourself instead?
That is as far as you go!
Committing evil deeds in a sacred place...
You are not getting away with this anymore!
In the name of the moon, I will punish you!
I can hear the crowd cheering me on.
We will have a fight to see who is the real champ!
I told you I am not!
I am the king of kings!
Please, Father, go back to being a normal priest!
A true boxer would never hit a beautiful young girl.
Instead, he would embrace her gently.
Knock out that snooty guy, too!
I see, so you are my next opponent!
One day, I will take it back from you!
We have to get that rainbow crystal back!
Now, I know my true identity.
It is okay, because Umino got hurt trying to save me.
I will go back to school starting tomorrow.
I asked you to come all the way out here
because I wanted to show you Usagi's good side, but...
But at least I have found out she is very caring about her friend.
Yume no naka futari de ita yo ne
Tomodachi no toki ni wa ki ni sezu
Anata dake ki ni naru shunkan ga atta no
Motto kirei ni i am about to sugu naritai
Koi suru to nanika ga kawaru ne
Dakishimeta tokimeki sono mama kono omoi tsutaetai
